## Interface: 30300
## Version: 2.0.0
## Title: Puppeteer
## Notes: Unit frames addon tailored for healers (3.3.5a / Ascension port)
## Author: OldManAlpha, Richard Truax(i2ichardt); Ascension port by mhaslinsky
## SavedVariables: PTGlobalOptions, PTHealCache, PTPlayerHealCache, PTRoleCache
## SavedVariablesPerCharacter: PTBindings, PTOptions

libs\LibStub\LibStub.lua
# Phase 2b: Entire Ace2 framework ripped (AceLibrary, AceLocale, AceOO, AceDebug, AceAddon,
# AceConsole, AceEvent, AceHook, Compost, Gratuity, RosterLib, Deformat, ItemBonusLib,
# Banzai, HealComm). PuppeteerLib replaced with frame-based dispatcher. Compost calls
# replaced with plain {} allocation; aggro via UnitThreatSituation; HealComm stubbed
# pending LibHealComm-4.0 wire-up in Phase 3.

# Phase 4: UnitProxy.lua removed. Multi-focus (focus2..focusN) was a SuperWoW-only
# custom-unit subsystem; native 3.3.5a focus is single-slot. Multi-focus deferred
# to v2.1; native single-slot focus restoration is part of that work.
